### Zenzi Z. Zenzic ###

Zenzi, XXXXXX
They lost to their best friend Polaris in the quarterfinals of the previous tournament, in a match so humiliating that many wondered if they would give up competing for good.
After an intense year of training, however, they're back and they're here to stay! Unlike the other fighters, they're convinced that there's some good left in Polaris, deep down.

Zenzi is a balanced fighter, a jack of all trades capable of going toe-to-toe with anyone.

### Specials ###
Squareshot: A shimmering square of energy that travels fast and hits hard.
Fourfold Flash: A powerful kick capable of annihalating an opponent's health.
Endless Eight: 

### Difficulty ###
Easy to play, low complexity. Recommended for beginners.